data.description: PRICE RANGE - SELLERS WILL ENTERTAIN OFFERS BETWEEN  $299,000-315,000.     Welcome to Aden Hills in West Mobile!  As you are welcomed into the home the foyer has split brick with an large Office on your right and a Formal Dining Room with wood flooring on your left.  The kitchen has plenty of cabinets for storage with stainless appliances (two years old) and beautiful granite countertops overlooking the dinette area with a bay window. Off the kitchen is your nice size laundry room with cabinets and a beautiful half bath. The large Master Bedroom is full of elegance with light streaming through the windows and double closets. The Master bath has a jetted tub and a separate stand up shower.  The Family Room is ready for your family with a fireplace and bookshelves. If you still need more room, walk out into the massive sunroom with windows everywhere that could be used for unlimited possibilities.  Upstairs is three additional bedrooms and a beautiful full bath with double vanities.  The covered back patio and custom built brick grill is ready and waiting for you to entertain. The back yard is fenced and has a nice shed.  This home has so much to see!  Call your favorite Realtor to view.
